# xbacklight
Do this if xbacklight doesn't change the display brightness (hardware). Place the `xorg.conf` file at `/etc/X11/xorg.conf`


# touch pad
Place the `40-libinput.conf` file at `/etc/X11/xorg.conf.d/` to configure scrolling and tap clicks.


# screen tearing
Place the `20-intel.conf` file at `/etc/X11/xorg.conf.d/` to prevent xorg screen tearing.

